author: Ariel Bogle And Tegan Taylor
title: What do these three things have to do with COVID-19? Not as much as the hype would suggest
description: We're all at home, anxious and online. There's also a flurry of research being published. It's fertile ground for the spread of misleading information about COVID-19.
content:
The pandemic is keeping many of us at home anxious and online. It's fertile ground for the spread of misleading information about COVID-19.
